2026-04-29T05:34:00.7850557Z 13    <!--
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7851367Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7905814Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7907053Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
