2026-04-29T05:34:00.7914214Z 22    <!--
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7914829Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7915601Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7916318Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7917193Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7918050Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7919116Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7919981Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7920885Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7921764Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7922718Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-29T05:34:00.7947914Z 33    -->
